  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deliver packages across the galaxy in this cute math-y puzzle game about timing, routes, and strange animal customers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What's Minuto about</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Minuto - Galactic Delivery</strong> is a puzzle game about syncing landings across planets.  <br>You draw paths, split your ship, and plan everything so your deliveries arrive all at once.  <br>There's obstacles, tricky turns, and carrots to get.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/67b6ea608a3ae2002cdc14934b66be79.poster.avif?t=1758924711\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/67b6ea608a3ae2002cdc14934b66be79.webm?t=1758924711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/67b6ea608a3ae2002cdc14934b66be79.mp4?t=1758924711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pixel place, pixel people</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s all wrapped in a colorful pixel art world.  <br>You’ll meet a lot of talkative animals—some friendly, some... less so.  <br>They have stories to tell, or complaints to file. Either way, you'll hear about it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/9b87d0ceda268b549757d577bb06243c.poster.avif?t=1758924711\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/9b87d0ceda268b549757d577bb06243c.webm?t=1758924711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/9b87d0ceda268b549757d577bb06243c.mp4?t=1758924711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Lore?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look closely, and there’s more going on than just deliveries.  <br>A few odd conversations, a few strange planets—maybe there’s a bigger picture underneath it all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/b62997e67be281e142e2813e5cb209ed.poster.avif?t=1758924711\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/b62997e67be281e142e2813e5cb209ed.webm?t=1758924711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/b62997e67be281e142e2813e5cb209ed.mp4?t=1758924711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You’ll like Minuto if:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You enjoy math-y, brain-y puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  You like chatting with random animals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You like a bit of hidden lore in your games  </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You won’t like it if:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You hate rabbits. You monster.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >That’s it, no other reason  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If that sounds like your kind of thing, buy it or add it to your wishlist.</strong>  <br>Minuto’s got work to do.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deliver packages across the galaxy in this cute math-y puzzle game about timing, routes, and strange animal customers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What's Minuto about</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Minuto - Galactic Delivery</strong> is a puzzle game about syncing landings across planets.  <br>You draw paths, split your ship, and plan everything so your deliveries arrive all at once.  <br>There's obstacles, tricky turns, and carrots to get.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/67b6ea608a3ae2002cdc14934b66be79.poster.avif?t=1758924711\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/67b6ea608a3ae2002cdc14934b66be79.webm?t=1758924711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/67b6ea608a3ae2002cdc14934b66be79.mp4?t=1758924711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pixel place, pixel people</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s all wrapped in a colorful pixel art world.  <br>You’ll meet a lot of talkative animals—some friendly, some... less so.  <br>They have stories to tell, or complaints to file. Either way, you'll hear about it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/9b87d0ceda268b549757d577bb06243c.poster.avif?t=1758924711\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/9b87d0ceda268b549757d577bb06243c.webm?t=1758924711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/9b87d0ceda268b549757d577bb06243c.mp4?t=1758924711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Lore?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look closely, and there’s more going on than just deliveries.  <br>A few odd conversations, a few strange planets—maybe there’s a bigger picture underneath it all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/b62997e67be281e142e2813e5cb209ed.poster.avif?t=1758924711\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/b62997e67be281e142e2813e5cb209ed.webm?t=1758924711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504540/extras/b62997e67be281e142e2813e5cb209ed.mp4?t=1758924711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You’ll like Minuto if:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You enjoy math-y, brain-y puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  You like chatting with random animals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You like a bit of hidden lore in your games  </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You won’t like it if:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You hate rabbits. You monster.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >That’s it, no other reason  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If that sounds like your kind of thing, buy it or add it to your wishlist.</strong>  <br>Minuto’s got work to do.</p>",
